==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Embattail
<hw>Em*bat"tail</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Embattle</er>.]</ety> <def>To furnish with battlements; to fortify
as with battlements.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To <qex>embattail</qex> and to wall about thy cause⟦br⟧
With iron-worded proof.</q> <rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Embattle</ent>⟦br⟧
